high_descs: Go across the room, go right, go to the fridge, turn left, go to the wall and turn left to the table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge and pick it back up.
Put the lettuce in the left side of the sink to the right of the two potatoes.
anns.task_desc: Put a head of chilled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: go forward to right side of black round table with lettuce
pick up lettuce from black table
turn around, go to white refrigerator
open refrigerator, place lettuce on top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up lettuce from refrigerator, close refrigerator
turn right, go to sink with two potatoes to the left
place lettuce to the left of two potatoes in sink
Walk forward to the table, take a right and walk to the fridge, take a left and go to the wall, take a left and face the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the left side of the table.
Turn left for one step, turn left for one step again, turn right for four steps and then turn left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, put the lettuce on the top shelf in the middle, shut the door for a few second, reopen the door, take the lettuce out, and shut the door again.
Turn around for one step, turn left and walk to the sinks, then turn left to face them.
Put the lettuce in the right sink to the left of the potatoes.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the sink.
